-1%201-1%208%201%208l1%202c1%204%207%209%2011%209%205%201%2010-1%2013-6l3-5c2-2%202-8%201-8l-3-5v-4h-8l-11-1-3-1m51%200v2l-1%203-2%205-1%202v7l3%204c5%2010%2018%2010%2023%200l3-4%201-6c-1%200-4-9-3-10l-8-1-11-1-4-1m49%206l-3%205c-2%200-1%206%201%209l2%202c0%202%206%208%209%209%205%201%2014-3%2016-9l2-4v-7c-1%200-2-2-2-5l-1-4h-16l-6-2-2%206m-153%201l-1%203c0%201%200%202-2%201s0%206%204%2012%208%209%2014%207c4-1%2010-7%2010-9l1-2%201-8c-1%200-2%200-2-4h-1l-1%204v4l-1%204c1%203%200%204-1%202h-1c0%203-15%202-16%200h-1c0%204-2-4-2-9s0-7-1-5\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          data-srcset=\"/blogs/static/99e705c81de4f4b392716c383b62ae53/ba381/apple-new-emoji-hair-options-2018-emojipedia.webp 200w,\n/blogs/static/99e705c81de4f4b392716c383b62ae53/7f61c/apple-new-emoji-hair-options-2018-emojipedia.webp 400w,\n/blogs/static/99e705c81de4f4b392716c383b62ae53/d00b9/apple-new-emoji-hair-options-2018-emojipedia.webp 800w,\n/blogs/static/99e705c81de4f4b392716c383b62ae53/92f8c/apple-new-emoji-hair-options-2018-emojipedia.webp 1200w,\n/blogs/static/99e705c81de4f4b392716c383b62ae53/fad48/apple-new-emoji-hair-options-2018-emojipedia.webp 1600w,\n/blogs/static/99e705c81de4f4b392716c383b62ae53/b84eb/apple-new-emoji-hair-options-2018-emojipedia.webp 2000w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/blogs/static/99e705c81de4f4b392716c383b62ae53/9c38a/apple-new-emoji-hair-options-2018-emojipedia.jpg 200w,\n/blogs/static/99e705c81de4f4b392716c383b62ae53/28275/apple-new-emoji-hair-options-2018-emojipedia.jpg 400w,\n/blogs/static/99e705c81de4f4b392716c383b62ae53/f67cc/apple-new-emoji-hair-options-2018-emojipedia.jpg 800w,\n/blogs/static/99e705c81de4f4b392716c383b62ae53/6e525/apple-new-emoji-hair-options-2018-emojipedia.jpg 1200w,\n/blogs/static/99e705c81de4f4b392716c383b62ae53/e735c/apple-new-emoji-hair-options-2018-emojipedia.jpg 1600w,\n/blogs/static/99e705c81de4f4b392716c383b62ae53/7ef33/apple-new-emoji-hair-options-2018-emojipedia.jpg 2000w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\"\n          data-src=\"/blogs/static/99e705c81de4f4b392716c383b62ae53/f67cc/apple-new-emoji-hair-options-2018-emojipedia.jpg\"\n          alt=\"apple new emoji hair options 2018 emojipedia\"\n          title=\"apple new emoji hair options 2018 emojipedia\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>而让我觉得骚的是，除了人支持肤色外，还有一些器官也支持了。🦵<em>0x1f9b5</em>🦶<em>0x1f9b6</em> 都能加上肤色。\n另外还有新的 emoji：🦸‍♀️ 🦸‍♂️，它是由基本的超级英雄 🦸(0x1f9b8) 加上性别符号 ♂️ <em>\\u{2642}\\u{fe0f}</em> ♀ ️<em>\\u{2641}\\u{fe0f}</em>。另外，除了超级英雄外，还有很多支持性别区分的 emoji，比如超级坏蛋 🦹。</p>\n<p>还有 🧙🧚🧛🧜🧝🧞🧟🧗🧘 这些都支持和性别组合。\n真的丧心病狂啊！</p>\n<h2 id=\"unicode-120\"><a href=\"#unicode-120\" aria-label=\"unicode 120 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Unicode 12.0</h2>\n<p>在明年的 12.0 里面还会包括很多更有意思的内容。它偏向于 accessibility，所以多了很多和这方面有关的元素。比如<strong>坐着轮椅的白色男人</strong>，助听器等等。也多出了手牵着手的 emoji，像这种白色的女人和黑色的男人握手 <a href=\"https://emojipedia.org/woman-and-man-holding-hands-light-skin-tone-dark-skin-tone/\">👩🏻‍🤝‍👨🏿</a>。除了异性之外，同性也有对应的 emoji，为 🌈 们提供骄傲。</p>\n<p>需要注意的是，握手如果是异性的话，左边的是女性右边的是男性，却没有左边是男性右边是女性的，这可能是出于对女性的尊重吧。然后再加上不同肤色的排列组合的话，就会多出 (!@#¥ 自己算吧 🌚）个看上去没上卵用的 emoji。</p>\n<p>关于更多 Emoji 12 的介绍，可以查看<a href=\"https://blog.emojipedia.org/230-new-emojis-in-final-list-for-2019/\">这篇文章</a>，这里面也出现了我提到的手拉手 emoji 的集合，让世界充满爱。</p>\n<div class=\"footnotes\">\n<hr>\n<ol>\n<li id=\"fn-1\">\n<p> 0x1f468</p>\n<a href=\"#fnref-1\" class=\"footnote-backref\">↩</a>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"title":"一些 Emoji 的有趣事情","spoiler":"🌈","date":"2019/05/19"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/emoji/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/toutiao/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"头条的对与错","spoiler":"头条没我想的那么坏"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/first-look-of-swiftui/first look of swiftui/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"对于 SwiftUI 的一些认识","spoiler":"在写了一些 SwiftUI 代码后的初级看法"}}}}}